Sum and Product Puzzle
An implementation of a solver for the Sum and Product Puzzle, with the capability to give some hints if the user wants to solve the puzzle themselves.

How to run:

1. Have python installed / install python (we used version 3.11.6, so try this one if other versions do not work) (check version in command lined using python --version)
2. Have pip installed / install it (we used version 23.3.2, optionally check with pip --version in the command line)
3. Use pip to install the python library ply (use "pip install ply" in the command line to install)
4. Open the command line in the folder this file is in then run the command "python parse_test.py"
5. Follow instructions of command line